{"title":"8 Panel Split Wall Set","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"bmw-m4-dominance-super-car-8-panel-split-wall-set","title":"BMW M4 DOMINANCE | Super Car | 8 Panel Split Wall Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"769\"\u003eBring \u003cstrong data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"452\"\u003ehigh-performance energy\u003c\/strong\u003e to your space with this \u003cstrong data-start=\"477\" data-end=\"513\"\u003eDOMINANCE 8-Panel Split Wall Set\u003c\/strong\u003e—a bold, modern composition built around a striking neon performance coupe, cinematic road scene, and aggressive typography. The design is split into \u003cstrong data-start=\"663\" data-end=\"690\"\u003e8 panels (4 × 2 layout)\u003c\/strong\u003e to create a premium, gallery-style wall look that instantly upgrades any room.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"771\" data-end=\"984\"\u003eThis artwork combines \u003cstrong data-start=\"793\" data-end=\"824\"\u003eclean automotive aesthetics\u003c\/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong data-start=\"826\" data-end=\"852\"\u003estreet-racing attitude\u003c\/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"896\"\u003eminimal yet powerful text elements\u003c\/strong\u003e—perfect for gamers, car lovers, creators, and anyone who likes their wall to feel fast.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"986\" data-end=\"1009\"\u003eWhat you’ll receive\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1185\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1047\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1047\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1032\"\u003e1 Set = 8 Panels\u003c\/strong\u003e (split design)\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"1048\" data-end=\"1109\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1050\" data-end=\"1109\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1050\" data-end=\"1071\"\u003eHigh-detail print\u003c\/strong\u003e with sharp textures + strong contrast\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-sta