nd classic car lovers\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1143\" data-end=\"1248\"\u003eBring the spirit of \u003cstrong data-start=\"1163\" data-end=\"1190\"\u003eAmerican muscle history\u003c\/strong\u003e to your wall with this legendary \u003cstrong data-start=\"1224\" data-end=\"1247\"\u003eShelby GT350 poster\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/article\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51518224957736,"sku":null,"price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51518224990504,"sku":null,"price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51518225023272,"sku":null,"price":799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/1966ShelbyMustangGT350MuscleCarWallArt8PanelSplitWallSet_1.jpg?v=1773060314"},{"product_id":"personalize-your-wall-space-8-panel-split-wall-set","title":"Personalize Your Wall Space | 8 Panel Split Wall Set","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTurn Your Favorite Photo into an 8-Panel Wall Setup\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCreate a stunning wall aesthetic with your own image, split into \u003cstrong\u003e8 perfectly aligned posters\u003c\/strong\u003e. Whether it’s your car, bike, memories, or aesthetic shots — this setup instantly upgrades your space.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow It Works\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUpload your image\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eWe split it into 8 panels\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eYou receive a complete wall-ready poster set\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ol\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat You Get\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e8 individual posters (1 image split into 